data.text:
The 11:14 Agency - Fireflies | 萤火虫 | Lucioles

(Fashion, Commercial)

A story promo for The 11:14 Agency’s new signing of model Quintana Hoyne inspired by her trilingual memories of her world travels growing up. Quintana looks for her past memories in a dreamy cityscape that blends time and presence.

Director, Concept, Writer: Waley Wang

Client: The 11:14 Agency

DP, Color, Edit: Alexey Kosorukov

Model/Starring: Quintana Hoyne

Featured model: Carty Caruso

Music by Ark Patrol

Sound Design/Mix: Chris Friedman

Production Design: Natalie Girsberger

Hair: Gabe Jenkins

Special Thanks: Denise Malik
